description:
We developed a hotel on Solana that everyone can join, but only SWH holders can build in it.

SWH holders can create their own rooms and events. They can also rent out their rooms or events to non-holders.

In SWH hotel, we have our own economy, where people can trade, buy, and sell rare items.

We have our very own NFT marketplace inside SWH hotel, where large projects would loved to be showcased.

People can put their complete NFT collection on display in their room and talk to potential buyers about what they have to offer.

You can see it as a platform where NFT fans from all over the world can get together and talk with each other, similar to Discord, but in a much more enjoyable way.
